      • initialize

        private void initialize()
        Gets the area elevation relative position. If the area has uniform sized polygons sets the probability value, uniform polygon label and value visible and irregular polygon label and value not visible. If has irregular polygon does the opposite. The default value for uniform are 10 and irregular is 100
